EN: The verbal agreement must be signed to take effect.

ZH: 老师常常用口头提醒学生们做作业。
EN: The teacher often verbally reminds the students to do their homework.

ZH: 双方还没有就这个问题进行过口头谈判。
EN: Both sides have not had verbal negotiations on this issue yet.

